# Skill GPS Frontend — Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your own key.
# NEVER commit the real `.env.local` file to Git!

# ── Groq API Key ──────────────────────────
# Used server-side by all Next.js API routes (/src/app/api/*).
# This key is NEVER exposed to the browser.
# Get a free key at: https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
